{"serial": "33079", "department_serial": 31, "code": "ME6096", "class": "*", "name": {"en": "Vehicle Dynamics", "ch": "車輛動力學"}, "notice": {"en": "", "ch": ""}, "instructor": {"en": ["Lin, Yuan-Ting"], "ch": ["林苑婷"]}, "credits": 3, "time_loc": [{"time": {"week": 3, "session": ["6", "7", "8"]}, "loc": {"building": "E2", "room": "306"}}], "isRequired": false, "isFullSem": false, "MaxStu": 25, "department": {"ch": "機械工程學系", "en": "Department of Mechanical Engineering"}, "system": {"ch": "碩博同修", "en": "Master/Doctoral Programme"}, "language": {"ch": "英語", "en": "English"}, "card": {"ch": "部份使用", "en": "Optional"}, "assigned": 11, "selected": 17, "remark": {"ch": "", "en": ""}, "goal": {"ch": "本課程主要以動力學觀點探討車輛的動態操控性能與穩定性能，該二種性能決定了汽車的安全性與商品性。首先介紹汽車底盤系統、車輛的操控性能指標以及其物理意義，然後介紹底盤各次系統的特性與這些性能指標的關係，再利用動態模型連結各項性能指標，以深入了解這些指標的理論基礎。最後，將介紹操控性能與穩定性能的客觀評價測試與解析方法。\n\n本課程為工程數學、自動控制及動力學等各學科的整合運用，期望以日常使用的車輛為平台，培養學生將機械相關理論應用實務問題的能力。於課程中，各重要動態模型將訓練學生撰寫Python或Matlab程式進行模擬分析，以培養下列能力：\n1.能夠發掘、分析工程問題，並且運用數學、科學、工程知識以及應用現代化工具、方法加以解決\n2.能夠規劃、設計與執行實驗，並且可以分析實驗結果與解釋數據所代表意義\n3.以程式語言實現車輛動態分析的邏輯以及數學運算的能力\n4.應用程式語言解決實務問題的能力\n5.簡報與書面報告的語言與文字論述的邏輯能力", "en": "This course mainly discusses the handling performance of the vehicle, which determine the safety and commerciality of a car. \n\nIn the course, the physical meaning of the vehicle’s handling performance, the relationship between the vehicle’s parameters and the handling performance will be introduced first, and then the theoretical basis of the performance indexes will be discussed through various simplified models. \n\nFinally, the control methods of the handling  performance, as well as the objective evaluation test and analysis methods will be introduced.\n\nThis course is an integrated application of concepts from various discipline such as engineering mathematics, automatic control, and dynamics. The lectures of the course will focus on the mechanism and physical implication of those phenomena experienced by daily use of vehicles."}, "outline": {"ch": "1. 認識車輛\n2. 車輛性能評價之理論與技術\n3. 車輛操控性與穩定性\n4. 輪胎動力學\n5. 轉向幾何與輪胎定位\n6. 縱向動態特性\n7. 轉向動態與性能\n8. 車輛整車模型與動態控制", "en": "1.  Introduction of Vehicle\n2. Objective evaluation of handling performance\n3.  Vehicle handling and stability\n4. Tire mechanics\n5. Steering geometry and wheel alignment\n6. Longitudinal dynamics\n7. Cornering characteristics\n8. Vehicle dynamics control"}, "textbook": {"ch": "1. 自編教材\n2. 參考書目：\n(1) Fundamentals of Vehicle Dynamics, Thomas D. Gillespie, Society of Automotive Engineers, 1992/2.\n(2) The Automotive Chassis, Second edition, J.Reimpell, H.Stoll, J.W.Betzler, Butterworth-Heinemann, 2001.", "en": "1. Self-made teaching materials\n2. Reference：\n(1) Fundamentals of Vehicle Dynamics, Thomas D. Gillespie, Society of Automotive Engineers, 1992/2.\n(2) The Automotive Chassis, Second edition, J.Reimpell, H.Stoll, J.W.Betzler, Butterworth-Heinemann, 2001."}, "selfCompiledRate": {"ch": "100%", "en": "100%"}, "instructMethod": {"ch": "講授", "en": ["Lecture"]}, "gradMethod": {"ch": "作業：40%\n期中、期末考：40%\n出席狀況與課堂表現：20%", "en": "Homework: 40%\nMidterm and Final Tests: 40%\nAttendance and Class Performance: 20%"}, "officeHour": {"ch": "By appointment", "en": "By appointment"}, "teachWeeks": {"ch": "17+1", "en": "17+1"}, "flexDiscription": {"ch": "輔以車輛設計相關活動", "en": "vehicle design-related activities"}, "domain": {"ch": "設計與分析", "en": "設計與分析"}, "map": {"ch": [{"competencies": "專業知識與技能", "rating": "(4)高", "assesments": ["紙筆測驗/會考", "作業練習", "專題研究報告(書面)", "出席/課堂表現"]}, {"competencies": "實驗規劃與資料分析", "rating": "(3)普通", "assesments": ["作業練習", "專題研究報告(書面)"]}, {"competencies": "工程設計與整合", "rating": "(4)高", "assesments": ["作業練習", "出席/課堂表現"]}, {"competencies": "合作溝通與管理", "rating": "(2)低", "assesments": ["出席/課堂表現"]}, {"competencies": "專業倫理與社會責任", "rating": "(3)普通", "assesments": ["作業練習", "專題研究報告(書面)", "出席/課堂表現"]}], "en": [{"competencies": "Engineering Knowledge and Problem Analysis", "rating": "(4)High", "assesments": ["Test/Exam", "Assignments", "Research Report(prin